==English==
===Etymology===
French [[agilité]], Latin [[agilitas]], fr. [[agilis]].

===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ʌˈʤɪl.ə.ti/

===Noun===
# The quality of being [[agile]]; the power of moving the [[limbs]] [[quick]]ly and easily; [[nimble]]ness; activity; quickness of [[motion]]; as, [[strength]] and agility of body.

